    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but existing in the middle of it is the hardest part. it's such a heavy way to live. if everything is just entropy and there's no actual point, then why do we even bother holding on so tight? it feels like we're just fighting an inevitable end that doesn't even care if we win or lose.",
